{"tid":1975572,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(CSGO免費左) 有無人有興趣玩社區服","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T08:16:41.000Z","uid":325375,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2c566d235576f2b12905201568b155bb5ae1dd02","tid":1975572,"uid":325375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"CSGO免費左之後 只要有STEAM就可以下載落黎玩<br />\n有人開左幾個SERVER<br />\n暫時有既模式 :  越獄模式 , 基地建造 , 休閒賽跑(cs1.6係叫死亡奔跑 或者叫陷阱ser) ,  滑水雜錦(滑水計時) 等等...<br />\n越獄模式IP : <a href=\"http://csgo.rs2online.com:27016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcsgo.rs2online.com%3A27016&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=450258ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">csgo.rs2online.com:27016</a><br />\n基地建造IP : <a href=\"http://csgo.rs2online.com:27018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcsgo.rs2online.com%3A27018&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=71d7db18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">csgo.rs2online.com:27018</a><br />\n休閒賽跑IP : <a href=\"http://csgo.rs2online.com:27019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcsgo.rs2online.com%3A27019&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=fe8ff40b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">csgo.rs2online.com:27019</a><br />\n滑水雜錦IP : <a href=\"http://csgo.rs2online.com:27021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcsgo.rs2online.com%3A27021&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=084ab547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">csgo.rs2online.com:27021</a><br />\n掛機SER IP : <a href=\"http://csgo.rs2online.com:27031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcsgo.rs2online.com%3A27031&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=8c7bacb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">csgo.rs2online.com:27031</a><br />\n<br />\n入社區服教學 :<br />\n[開左GAME之後 禁 &quot;進行CS:GO&quot; 然後 官方遊戲配對果度有個向下箭咀 禁落去 簡 &quot;瀏覽社群伺服器&quot; 打開之後 禁 &quot;新增伺服器&quot; 輸入上邊你想玩既IP 然後 禁 &quot;把此位置加入我的最愛&quot; 服務器就會加入到最愛 最後就可以入到SERVER]<br />\n<br />\n下邊個網比懶人用 入去直接禁 &quot;連接到伺服器&quot; 就可以直接入到SERVER<br />\n<a href=\"http://proconfig.moedaze.com/csgoser/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproconfig.moedaze.com%2Fcsgoser%2F&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=71d4c36e\" target=\"_blank\">http://proconfig.moedaze.com/csgoser/</a>"},{"pid":"c45d4858aee57b17e041137a955622a56b815ce7","tid":1975572,"uid":121984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccf094c0ff449e9a5de8d81af97feaeaf79ae9a","tid":1975572,"uid":343502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"ProConfig......大更新完之後就變咗掠水程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW個越獄ser好多小學雞搞事又冇admin解決下，點玩"},{"pid":"97f5a45591639e5712c472e68f6585d00bfc51eb","tid":1975572,"uid":186265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ccf094c0ff449e9a5de8d81af97feaeaf79ae9a","tid":1975572,"uid":343502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"ProConfig......大更新完之後就變咗掠水程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW個越獄ser好多小學雞搞事又冇admin解決下，點玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T18:20:38.000Z","msg":"掠水?<br />\n所有功能基本免費, 贊助都只係可以微調功能+唔洗看幾十秒毒L圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n效果大不如前係事實, 比如 PUBG 左限又限, 無得改 config 情況下100fps 升到 15-20fps 我都盡晒力(以前升60架...)<br />\n就算以前有贊助過都可以用晒新版所有功能, 得幾百人用贊助得幾%都無(仲送左好多出去)<br />\n仲要成日有人R個會員試用... 都 99.9999% 效果比晒你試... 我都直接覆無效果不要贊助,怕麻煩<br />\n---<br />\n小學雞搞事事小, 有班人跟足規貼來捉先煩<br />\nbtw Server 銀幣可以同我玩換 proconfig 程式條 key, 唔好話我掠水, 玩就比你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503d33c43